OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: 45-minute wait      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwarning as school buses    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fface disruption            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some pupils have been warned they may  
OL,6, face a wait of up to 45 minutes for the
OL,7, school bus because of a shortage of bus
OL,8, drivers and passenger assistants.      
OL,10,FRhondda Cynon Taf council leader Andrew
OL,11,FMorgan said school bus services face   
OL,12,Fdisruption because of the number of    
OL,13,Fdrivers and assistants self-isolating. 
OL,15,FHe said services were experiencing     
OL,16,F"severe difficulties" and the council  
OL,17,Fare working to minimise delays.        
OL,19,FHe said pressure on councils was "at   
OL,20,Fits worst" since the pandemic began.   
